{"id": 1816, "genre": 1001, "title": "说起来，你想给MUJI提点什么意见？", "description": "也包括它最近跨界搞的那些副业。(题图来自Pixabay)", "record_count": 4888, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170724170454j5IvDCA61fmQXtzW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-28T03:00:31Z", "options": [{"id": 228611, "content": "来个友善点的价位吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1101706}, {"id": 227076, "content": "各位莘莘学子，各位辛劳的妈妈们，还有各位办公室人员，不管您是哪种身份，只要您有空余的时 间，那么这份工作一定适合您【日挣100--200块钱】， 别再犹豫喽，赶快卫鑫:yy236697", "image": "img/option/option/201708032234093i0xz7DfoawtFsI9", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095526}, {"id": 225802, "content": "木有意见，离开中国好不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091908}, {"id": 228109, "content": "便宜点啥都好说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663496}, {"id": 225296, "content": "贵，所以我连棉花糖都没买一包", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002857}, {"id": 225297, "content": "便宜一点？", "image": null, "praise_count": 374, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839742}, {"id": 225298, "content": "好想再吃一次汽水糖…可是太贵了哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459423}, {"id": 225299, "content": "啥是muji？母鸡？它很厉害吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003934}, {"id": 225300, "content": "嗯，，，果然更喜欢小妖的风格啊~~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068667}, {"id": 225301, "content": "敢不敢便宜一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 203, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090422}, {"id": 229141, "content": "产品能不能有点新意啊？感觉把十年以前的产品拿出来和当季热卖款并无区别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103601}, {"id": 225302, "content": "推出新品的节奏敢快一点么？除了衣服其他都是老三样，儿。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260895}, {"id": 225303, "content": "太贵了 买不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 126, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925534}, {"id": 225815, "content": "店面更规整", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092344}, {"id": 225305, "content": "能不能价格友善点？", "image": null, "praise_count": 434, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042334}, {"id": 231705, "content": "供休息的沙发多一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 225306, "content": "款式在多一点吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080494}, {"id": 225307, "content": "性价比敢不敢再高一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596249}, {"id": 225308, "content": "取消塑料製品。", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651000}, {"id": 225309, "content": "便宜一点还叫MUJI？", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015340}, {"id": 225310, "content": "天朝旗舰店的服务有一半是保安在干！", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777364}, {"id": 225311, "content": "一样的东西尤其是衣服到底要卖多少年啊……稍微有点新东西吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 207, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713001}, {"id": 225312, "content": "文具品类再多一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691679}, {"id": 225313, "content": "哈哈哈哈被出家的那位笑死了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988729}, {"id": 225569, "content": "如果说可能的话，希望在有能力的三线城市也多开几家分店。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984774}, {"id": 225314, "content": "讲真服务也是在走冷淡风吗态度真不怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067205}, {"id": 225570, "content": "雖然定價差不多 但是在英國卻顯得很友善", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087068}, {"id": 225572, "content": "基本出去旅游只要有muji的城市都会去看看，旅行箱更是看了不知道多少遍的东西..基本进去都是摸摸...去了日本才发现，同样的产品，在日本几乎是家庭主妇经常去买的，到了国内反倒只是眼馋的份儿。??", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892141}, {"id": 227620, "content": "潮牌..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293316}, {"id": 225317, "content": "中日同价吧！！即使这样也有点贵，但总比现在好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 190, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846204}, {"id": 225573, "content": "不讲价就是卖傻子的嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 362598}, {"id": 225574, "content": "关注性价比", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921463}, {"id": 225319, "content": "除了价格还是价格", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660375}, {"id": 225575, "content": "横格本里的横线间隔敢不敢大一点！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089179}, {"id": 227367, "content": "希望在中国能更加普及一点 ，每个城市如果都能有就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087593}, {"id": 225320, "content": "太土 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981279}, {"id": 225576, "content": "网易严选和米家有品要超过你们了", "image": "img/option/option/20170729080849CBZeYE89hwSp3dQV", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628049}, {"id": 227624, "content": "贵就算了还不咋地。看得起也是因为包装得好“看起来好像很高档的样子”其实质量一般 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002375}, {"id": 225577, "content": "有双很舒服的拖鞋，在哪都买不到，很久了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78222}, {"id": 225578, "content": "我说完了muji看的到么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091222}, {"id": 225323, "content": "降价", "image": null, "praise_count": 165, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764107}, {"id": 227115, "content": "不要去卖菜了。好好做衣服吧，有点非性冷淡的趋势也是好的！?", "image": "img/option/option/20170804043617QeEouSH1ptbdyOz8", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75333}, {"id": 225324, "content": "衣服年轻些，增加种类，例如休闲的背包、斜挎包", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869069}, {"id": 225580, "content": "降价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840816}, {"id": 225836, "content": "价格", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000533}, {"id": 225328, "content": "进入中国市场这么多年，老实讲muji的性冷淡高端感已经没了…在华希望价格更亲民一些吧毕竟也不是真的好东西…基本款看看真的厌烦有的时候…", "image": null, "praise_count": 151, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600190}, {"id": 225585, "content": "平民的东西，贵族的价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979444}, {"id": 225330, "content": "贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791235}, {"id": 225331, "content": "价格能正常点吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893456}, {"id": 225332, "content": "muji是啥……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015307}]}